3. 实现一个名为 odd-or-even 的 Bash function，可以用来判断给其提供的第一个参数是奇数还是偶数，奇数时输出 odd，偶数时输出 even

#!/bin/bash
read -p "number" first last
echo first: $first
if [ `expr $first % 2` -eq 0 ];
then 
echo "even number"
else 
echo "odd number"
fi


result：

wenshi@LAPTOP-5GG7LHTM:~/gtb-git-remote/homework-clibasic$ oddtest1.sh
number 98 99
first: 98
even number
wenshi@LAPTOP-5GG7LHTM:~/gtb-git-remote/homework-clibasic$ oddtest1.sh
number 10000 1000009 1222222 8999993
first: 10000
even number
wenshi@LAPTOP-5GG7LHTM:~/gtb-git-remote/homework-clibasic$ oddtest1.sh
